Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.99,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(We！ Are！ STAR☆T☆RAIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:12.32,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(Check！ Now！ Come on！ Come on！ Come on！ Come on！)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.56,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(We！ Are！ STAR☆T☆RAIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.98,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}B小町！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.06,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}難しいこと考えるよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.84,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}もっとスウィートな愛を感じてたいの！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.54,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}良いも悪いも見た目じゃね？(見た目じゃね？)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:31.27,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大人しそうなほど騙されるの！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.74,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Be All Right　今は運に身を任せ　Ah……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.74,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(いつもそうさ　一瞬が勝負)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.76,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Be All Right　君はどっちが良い？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:46.15,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大切なことはそう見えないの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:50.32,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そうこれはSTAR☆T☆RAIN　乗っていこうよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.73,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}きっとずっと　止まらないから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.82,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ手を上げて　振り回して
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.06,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}まだまだ行くよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:02.97,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}そうこれがSTAR☆T☆RAIN　もっと騒いで！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:06.53,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}きっとずっと　終わらないから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.61,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}さあ手を上げて　振り回して
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:15.38,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}もっと騒いで楽しみたい君と
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.42,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(We！ Are！ STAR☆T☆RAIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.74,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(Check！ Now！ Come on！ Come on！ Come on！ Come on！)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:25.90,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(We！ Are！ STAR☆T☆RAIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.99,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(We! Are! STAR☆T☆RAIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:12.32,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(Check! Now! Come on! Come on! Come on! Come on!)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:15.56,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(We! Are! STAR☆T☆RAIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.98,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}B小町!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:21.06,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}與其思考困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:24.84,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我更想感受甜美的愛!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:27.54,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好與壞不都是表面? (不都是表面?)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.54,0:04:31.27,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}越是老實越會被欺騙!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:34.74,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Be all right  現在把自己交給運氣  Ah……
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:37.74,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(總是這樣  一瞬間分出高下)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:40.76,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}Be all right  你覺得哪一個比較好?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:46.15,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}最重要的東西是看不見的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.15,0:04:50.32,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}沒錯  這就是星光☆列☆車  快上車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:53.73,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一路行進  直到永遠  都不會停止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.82,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舉起手來  揮起圈來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:04:59.06,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我們還要繼續向前!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:05:02.97,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}沒錯  這就是星光☆列☆車  歡呼起來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:06.53,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}一路高歌  直到永遠  都不會結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:09.61,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}舉起手來  揮起圈來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:15.38,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}我想和你繼續歡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:19.42,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(We! Are! STAR☆T☆RAIN)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:22.74,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(Check! Now! Come on! Come on! Come on! Come on! )
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.87,0:05:25.90,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}(We! Are! STAR☆T☆RAIN)
